Class DoctorController

java.lang.Object
controllers.DoctorController
public class DoctorController extends Object
The DoctorController class manages the interaction between a logged-in Doctor and the system, comprising the logic for handling the following features available to the Doctor: 1. View Patient Medical Records 2. Update Patient Medical Records 3. View Personal Schedule 4. Set Availability for Appointments 5. Accept or Decline Appointment Requests 6. View Upcoming Appointments 7. Record Appointment Outcome 8. Logout
